120
0:05:47.434,000 --> 0:05:49,000
was to look around and see: What are the abundant resources

121
0:05:50.233,000 --> 0:05:51,000
in these developing world contexts?

122
0:05:51.957,000 --> 0:05:52,000
And what they noticed was,

123
0:05:53.246,000 --> 0:05:56,000
