0:09:38.412,000 --> 0:09:42,000
We've heard a lot recently about hunch and instinct

209
0:09:42.967,000 --> 0:09:45,000
and blink-like sudden moments of clarity,

210
0:09:46.092,000 --> 0:09:5,000
