0:16:53.978,000 --> 0:16:55,000
in the last day or last week, right?

376
0:16:56.81,000 --> 0:16:59,000
(Applause)

377
0:17:00.107,000 --> 0:17:01,000
And that, I think,

378
0:17:01.703,000 --> 0:17:03,000
is a great case study, a great lesson

379
0:17:04.276,000 --> 0:17:08,000
in the power -- the marvelous, unplanned, emergent, unpredictable power --

380
0:17:09.244,000 --> 0:17:1,000
of open innovative systems.

381
0:17:11.262,000 --> 0:17:12,000
When you build them right,

382
0:17:12.526,000 --> 0:17:14,000
they will be led to completely new directions

